Agent thing on devices and presences	-	Emissary
Thing Emissary submits requests to 	-	Conduit
Thing for controlling house things 	-	Caretaker

Emissary
	- libemissary
	- libemissary-pocketsphinx
	- emissary-application
	- emissary-desktop-application
	- emissary-panel-application

Conduit
	- libconduit
	- libconduit-apiai
	- conduit-application
	
Caretaker
	- caretaker-application
	- caretaker-soundandmusic
	- caretaker-spotify
	- caretaker-lighting
	- caretaker-hue

H: "Turn living room big lights on"
==> emissary hears
==> sends to speech recognition
==> sends results to apiai*
==> apiai calls conduit with result
==> conduit calls caretaker to request the lights

